        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594a08_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』我時復為說最上法，示教利喜。",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594a09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如其所應示教利喜已，我於爾時，隱身不現。",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594a10_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我雖如是隱其身相，彼眾亦悉不能知覺，復起疑念：",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594a11_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『適所隱者，為沙門邪？",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594a12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "婆羅門邪？",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594a12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或天、人、魔、梵邪？",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594a12_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594a12_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我時現自身相與彼同等，彼眾尚猶不能見我，況復超勝我？",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594a14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時所說最上法者，所謂最勝神通知見，餘之長者、沙門、四大王天、忉利天及魔眾會，亦復如是！",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594a16_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594a17_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我昔曾往無數百千梵天會中，隨彼眾會何等色相，我亦同彼現其形相；",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594a18_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
