    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時所說最上法者，所謂最勝神通知見。",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594b01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594b01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼長者子，於如是事，雖知雖見，以不信故，乃發是言，而為誹謗。",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594b02_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由彼心言及彼所見，相續謗故，速墮地獄。",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594b03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594b04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其有地獄所行之道、所趣業因，乃至有情所受報應，我悉如實一一了知；",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594b05_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復畜生所行之道、所趣業因，乃至有情所受報應，悉如實知；",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594b07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復餓鬼所行之道、所趣業因，乃至有情所受報應，悉如實知；",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594b08_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有阿修羅道、人所行道、天所行道所趣業因，乃至彼彼有情所受報應，悉如實知。",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594b10_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594b10_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至于涅槃所行聖道，及涅槃法，乃至有情證涅槃果，悉如實知。",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594b12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594b12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼長者子，於如是事，雖知雖見，以不信故，乃發是言，而為誹謗。",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594b13_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由彼心言及彼所見，相續謗故，速墮地獄。",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594b14_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說身毛喜豎經卷上",
        "from": "T17n0757_001:0594b15_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]